headline: Should J. M. Smucker's New High-Protein Uncrustables Prompt a Fresh Look From SJM Investors?
summary: In September 2025, J. M. Smucker announced the nationwide launch of two new high-protein Uncrustables® sandwiches, Bright-Eyed Berry™ and Up & Apple™, offering 12 grams of protein per serving, more fiber and whole grains, and no high-fructose corn syrup or artificial sweeteners, aimed at health-conscious, busy consumers. This expansion into functional, protein-rich snack options highlights Smucker’s adaptation to evolving consumer demands for convenient and nutritious foods, even as other...
